Summary: Groundedness & hallucination detection — multi-tier cascade (consensus + lexical + semantic + NLI + LLM-judge), preventive citations, multimodal verification, explainable evidence, audit-grade Merkle proofs. Consumer-agnostic; embedding / NLI / LLM judge are injected.
